# types

**Instance Property**

An array of uniform type identifier strings of the data types that the receiver supports.

## Declaration

```swift
var types: [NSPasteboard.PasteboardType] { get }
```

## Getting types

- **availableType(from:)**: Returns from a given array of types the first type within the pasteboard item, according to the ordering of types.
